      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TEST THE LAW (2) has returned in good order this prep and looks ready to put it all together fourth-up. Meets VAN ROY 2.5kgs better this time after finishing hot on his heels two back and has been kept up to the mark with two sharp trials since his narrow third-up fourth. Ready. VAN ROY (5) is king of the Country Cups circuit and finds another suitable one to add to his mantle. Has already taken out a few heats of the Limestone Cup Series, most recently victor of the Penola Cup. Has the runs on the board, will just need a touch of luck from the draw. ASTRADEEL (4) was a barnstorming winner at Warrnambool first-up. Has more to offer. Warrnambool Cup winner ANY LUCK (1) also needs to be included.",
